pecific application<br> at hand. All the corrections presented are independent on the technique used in the<br> static design of the device. Preliminary numerical results are obtained in the scattering abatement<br> (cloaking) of obstacle with simple geometries. The numerical simulations are obtained using an<br> original, general integral formulation of the problem, solved using an extended boundary element<br> method.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
