carried out on the -20 degree inlet to understand the effects of lip shaping at high speed (Mach 0.8). An encouraging equivalence has been achieved between the datum and scarfed inlet and further detailed work (internal surfaces) leading to experiments has been recommended. Work is needed on scarf angle choice.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
