d flow separation by up to 10° in AOA. Overall, slotted airfoils demonstrated superior performance over clean airfoils at higher AOAs, making them particularly beneficial for vertical-axis wind turbine blade applications.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
