 in good agreement with measurements. Unsteady loading noise is found dominant for all tones for the present rotor-beam configuration corresponding to a small chord-to-beam diameter ratio. The three-dimensional directivities of some sound harmonics also have a unique wavy pattern in the rotor plane."}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
