ed fan test rig, and total pressure and static pressure measurements are recorded with a 5-hole Aero-Probe. The research results indicate that the fan experiment is successful in capturing this steady flow distortion. Both droop and scarf type intakes cause minor steady flow distortion at the outlet of the intake, which rapidly decays in the duct.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
