ic, intake geometry with non-uniform inflow and a realistic buzz-saw noise source. The results of this simulation are compared with results from a conventional full-span calculation. The approximation provides a significant saving in computational expense and successfully captures much of the acoustic content of interest.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
