proposed that an optimal design, encompassing both aerodynamic performance and reduced acoustic impact, can be achieved at design flow coefficients between ϕd=0.75 and ϕd=0.90."}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
