redicted to decrease by nearly 10 dB/Hz. Other relevant geometric features are the mounting beam and the guide elements, which are responsible for flow-borne noise emissions near 698 Hz and 2699 Hz, respectively.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
