 of the compressor while effectively suppressing characteristic frequency bands induced by the unsteady fluctuation of tip leakage flow.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
