s, challenges remain in fully optimizing these methods for diverse operating conditions and ensuring their practical application. This review highlights promising strategies for improving flow control efficiency and robustness, contributing to the design of next-generation turbomachinery.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
