 the influence of rotor blade position on aerodynamic performance is relatively minor. However, placing the rotor at the duct exit position proves advantageous for improving the aerodynamic distribution characteristics of the system.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
