ier design. • Highlights underdeveloped safety concepts for maritime hydrogen transport. • Proposes a framework to enhance risk management practices. • Contributes to global decarbonization through safer hydrogen transport. • Provides insights for future maritime hydrogen regulations.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
