e test rig configuration, provides guidance for wind tunnel testing, and lays a foundation for subsequent unsteady coupled fan–intake studies.'}], 'model': 'deepseek-chat', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.2}}
